casting_Corporation\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"their own slightly skewed style\", \"from\": 49, \"to\": 80}, {\"ngram\": \"the games\", \"from\": 84, \"to\": 93}, {\"ngram\": \"cheese singles\", \"from\": 107, \"to\": 121}, {\"ngram\": \"rugby league\", \"from\": 142, \"to\": 154}, {\"ngram\": \"an Olympic sport\", \"from\": 161, \"to\": 177}, {\"ngram\": \"the prayers\", \"from\": 188, \"to\": 199}, {\"ngram\": \"a world\", \"from\": 203, \"to\": 210}, {\"ngram\": \"too much sport\", \"from\": 217, \"to\": 231}, {\"ngram\": \"Rampaging Roy Slaven\", \"from\": 263, \"to\": 283}, {\"ngram\": \"the doyen\", \"from\": 286, \"to\": 295}, {\"ngram\": \"dominatrix\", \"from\": 300, \"to\": 310}, {\"ngram\": \"satirical sportscasting\", \"from\": 314, \"to\": 337}, {\"ngram\": \"People\", \"from\": 398, \"to\": 404}, {\"ngram\": \"Medals\", \"from\": 406, \"to\": 412}, {\"ngram\": \"Cheese\", \"from\": 417, \"to\": 423}]}, {\"sentence\": \"After earning the ire of former prime minister John Howard with their late-90s variety show Club Buggery, Roy & HG (and their mascotFatso, the Fat-Arsed Wombat) hit the big time withThe Dream, their skewed take on Sydney's 2000 Olympic Games.\", \"from\": 427, \"to\": 669, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 474, \"end\": 485, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/John_Howard\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 7.055252643503789e-19, \"text\": \"John Howard\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/John_Howard\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/John_Howard\"}, {\"begin\": 519, \"end\": 531, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Club_Buggery\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Club Buggery\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\", \"Q15416\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Club_Buggery\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Club_Buggery\"}, {\"begin\": 641, \"end\": 647, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sydney\", \"score\": 0.9999999999995453, \"rank\": 4.1649878130616815e-13, \"text\": \"Sydney\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sydney\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sydney\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the ire\", \"from\": 441, \"to\": 448}, {\"ngram\": \"their late-90s variety\", \"from\": 491, \"to\": 513}, {\"ngram\": \"Roy\", \"from\": 533, \"to\": 536}, {\"ngram\": \"HG\", \"from\": 539, \"to\": 541}, {\"ngram\": \"their mascotFatso\", \"from\": 547, \"to\": 564}, {\"ngram\": \"the Fat-Arsed Wombat\", \"from\": 566, \"to\": 586}, {\"ngram\": \"the big time\", \"from\": 592, \"to\": 604}, {\"ngram\": \"Dream\", \"from\": 613, \"to\": 618}, {\"ngram\": \"their skewed take\", \"from\": 620, \"to\": 637}]}, {\"sentence\": \"They spoke to Guardian Australia, in character and under armed guard, to discuss the future of equestrian events, Gina Rinehart's swimming prowess and the prospect of a World Origin.\", \"from\": 671, \"to\": 853, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 685, \"end\": 703, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Guardian_Australia\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Guardian Australia\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\", \"Q234460\", \"Q11032\", \"Q1092563\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Guardian_Australia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Guardian_Australia\"}, {\"begin\": 766, \"end\": 776, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Equestrianism\", \"score\": 0.9999999991177901, \"rank\": 8.819140889640725e-10, \"text\": \"equestrian\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Equestrianism\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Equestrianism\"}, {\"begin\": 785, \"end\": 798, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gina_Rinehart\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Gina Rinehart\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gina_Rinehart\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gina_Rinehart\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"character\", \"from\": 708, \"to\": 717}, {\"ngram\": \"armed guard\", \"from\": 728, \"to\": 739}, {\"ngram\": \"the future\", \"from\": 752, \"to\": 762}, {\"ngram\": \"the prospect\", \"from\": 822, \"to\": 834}, {\"ngram\": \"a World Origin\", \"from\": 838, \"to\": 852}]}, {\"sentence\": \"So is People, Medals and Cheese a continuation of The Dream?\", \"from\": 855, \"to\": 915, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"People\", \"from\": 861, \"to\": 867}, {\"ngram\": \"Medals\", \"from\": 869, \"to\": 875}, {\"ngram\": \"Cheese\", \"from\": 880, \"to\": 886}, {\"ngram\": \"a continuation\", \"from\": 887, \"to\": 901}, {\"ngram\": \"The Dream\", \"from\": 905, \"to\": 914}]}, {\"sentence\": \"HG Nelson: No, I do not think so, because People, Medals and Cheese is radio only.\", \"from\": 917, \"to\": 999, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 917, \"end\": 926, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Roy_and_HG\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.285496828750102e-34, \"text\": \"HG Nelson\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q483501\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Roy_and_HG\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Roy_and_HG\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"People\", \"from\": 959, \"to\": 965}, {\"ngram\": \"Medals\", \"from\": 967, \"to\": 973}, {\"ngram\": \"Cheese\", \"from\": 978, \"to\": 984}, {\"ngram\": \"radio\", \"from\": 988, \"to\": 993}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But that gives us a licence to put the theatre of the mind front and centre.\", \"from\": 1000, \"to\": 1076, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"us\", \"from\": 1015, \"to\": 1017}, {\"ngram\": \"a licence\", \"from\": 1018, \"to\": 1027}, {\"ngram\": \"the theatre\", \"from\": 1035, \"to\": 1046}, {\"ngram\": \"the mind front\", \"from\": 1050, \"to\": 1064}, {\"ngram\": \"centre\", \"from\": 1069, \"to\": 1075}]}, {\"sentence\": \"We can paint a picture with words in a way that makes it seem much more scandalous and impossible to understand what possessed a triple gold medallist tobash the living daylights out of a horse.\", \"from\": 1077, \"to\": 1271, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a picture\", \"from\": 1090, \"to\": 1099}, {\"ngram\": \"words\", \"from\": 1105, \"to\": 1110}, {\"ngram\": \"a way\", \"from\": 1114, \"to\": 1119}, {\"ngram\": \"a triple gold medallist\", \"from\": 1204, \"to\": 1227}, {\"ngram\": \"the living daylights\", \"from\": 1235, \"to\": 1255}, {\"ngram\": \"a horse\", \"from\": 1263, \"to\": 1270}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Is there still a place for equestrian events at the Olympics?\", \"from\": 1273, \"to\": 1334, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1300, \"end\": 1310, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Equestrianism\", \"score\": 0.9999999991177901, \"rank\": 8.819140889640725e-10, \"text\": \"equestrian\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Equestrianism\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Equestrianism\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a place\", \"from\": 1288, \"to\": 1295}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympics\", \"from\": 1321, \"to\": 1333}]}, {\"sentence\": \"We can not have athletes flogging a live horse on television, can we?\", \"from\": 1335, \"to\": 1404, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"athletes\", \"from\": 1351, \"to\": 1359}, {\"ngram\": \"a live horse\", \"from\": 1369, \"to\": 1381}, {\"ngram\": \"television\", \"from\": 1385, \"to\": 1395}]}, {\"sentence\": \"HG: I can hear the irony in your voice there.\", \"from\": 1406, \"to\": 1451, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the irony\", \"from\": 1421, \"to\": 1430}, {\"ngram\": \"your voice\", \"from\": 1434, \"to\": 1444}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Look, my take on this is how many countries can even afford, firstly, the clobber they wear - the jodhpurs, the dress jackets \\u2026 Roy Slaven: The boots \\u2026 HG: The boots; the hat.\", \"from\": 1452, \"to\": 1629, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"my take\", \"from\": 1458, \"to\": 1465}, {\"ngram\": \"how many countries\", \"from\": 1477, \"to\": 1495}, {\"ngram\": \"Roy Slaven\", \"from\": 1580, \"to\": 1590}, {\"ngram\": \"The boots\", \"from\": 1592, \"to\": 1601}, {\"ngram\": \"HG\", \"from\": 1604, \"to\": 1606}, {\"ngram\": \"The boots\", \"from\": 1608, \"to\": 1617}, {\"ngram\": \"the hat\", \"from\": 1619, \"to\": 1626}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Let alone buy a horse!\", \"from\": 1630, \"to\": 1652, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a horse\", \"from\": 1644, \"to\": 1651}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Most of these horses are worth upwards of $1m, never mind the horse float that they need to go in.\", \"from\": 1653, \"to\": 1751, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"these horses\", \"from\": 1661, \"to\": 1673}, {\"ngram\": \"$1m\", \"from\": 1695, \"to\": 1698}, {\"ngram\": \"the horse float\", \"from\": 1711, \"to\": 1726}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Roy: I think the argument for dog races at theOlympic Gamesis far more compelling than for equestrian.\", \"from\": 1753, \"to\": 1855, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1844, \"end\": 1854, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Equestrianism\", \"score\": 0.9999999991177901, \"rank\": 8.819140889640725e-10, \"text\": \"equestrian\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Equestrianism\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Equestrianism\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the argument\", \"from\": 1766, \"to\": 1778}, {\"ngram\": \"dog races\", \"from\": 1783, \"to\": 1792}, {\"ngram\": \"theOlympic Gamesis\", \"from\": 1796, \"to\": 1814}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Sure, you are not sitting on a dog, but you are training a dog to express itself at very high speeds over short distances.\", \"from\": 1856, \"to\": 1978, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a dog\", \"from\": 1885, \"to\": 1890}, {\"ngram\": \"a dog\", \"from\": 1913, \"to\": 1918}, {\"ngram\": \"very high speeds\", \"from\": 1940, \"to\": 1956}, {\"ngram\": \"short distances\", \"from\": 1962, \"to\": 1977}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I think that's something that people can relate to.\", \"from\": 1979, \"to\": 2030, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"something\", \"from\": 1994, \"to\": 2003}, {\"ngram\": \"people\", \"from\": 2009, \"to\": 2015}]}, {\"sentence\": \"All you need is a bit of flat track, and a dog.\", \"from\": 2031, \"to\": 2078, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a bit\", \"from\": 2047, \"to\": 2052}, {\"ngram\": \"flat track\", \"from\": 2056, \"to\": 2066}, {\"ngram\": \"a dog\", \"from\": 2072, \"to\": 2077}]}, {\"sentence\": \"HG: And meat.\", \"from\": 2080, \"to\": 2093, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"HG\", \"from\": 2080, \"to\": 2082}, {\"ngram\": \"meat\", \"from\": 2088, \"to\": 2092}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The question on everyone's lips is: what happened to Fatso?\", \"from\": 2095, \"to\": 2154, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2148, \"end\": 2153, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ghostly_Trio\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.887622192788926e-15, \"text\": \"Fatso\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ghostly_Trio\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ghostly_Trio\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The question\", \"from\": 2095, \"to\": 2107}, {\"ngram\": \"everyone's lips\", \"from\": 2111, \"to\": 2126}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Will he be joining you in Paris?\", \"from\": 2155, \"to\": 2187, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2181, \"end\": 2186, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999999972715, \"rank\": 2.729179497675448e-12, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Does the ABC have sufficient funding to buy him back from Kerry Stokes?\", \"from\": 2188, \"to\": 2259, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2197, \"end\": 2200, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australian_Broadcasting_Corporation\", \"score\": 0.9999999855094758, \"rank\": 1.4490359921970776e-08, \"text\": \"ABC\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australian_Broadcasting_Corporation\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australian_Broadcasting_Corporation\"}, {\"begin\": 2246, \"end\": 2258, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kerry_Stokes\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Kerry Stokes\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kerry_Stokes\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kerry_Stokes\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"sufficient funding\", \"from\": 2206, \"to\": 2224}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Roy: Well, each city comes up with its own mascot, and in this instance it's the Olympic Phryge, which is a terrific thing.\", \"from\": 2261, \"to\": 2384, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"each city\", \"from\": 2272, \"to\": 2281}, {\"ngram\": \"its own mascot\", \"from\": 2296, \"to\": 2310}, {\"ngram\": \"this instance\", \"from\": 2319, \"to\": 2332}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympic Phryge\", \"from\": 2338, \"to\": 2356}, {\"ngram\": \"a terrific thing\", \"from\": 2367, \"to\": 2383}]}, {\"sentence\": \"They took a small hat, put some legs and feet under it and they have created a very engaging little character that says very little to a lot of people.\", \"from\": 2385, \"to\": 2536, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a small hat\", \"from\": 2395, \"to\": 2406}, {\"ngram\": \"some legs\", \"from\": 2412, \"to\": 2421}, {\"ngram\": \"feet\", \"from\": 2426, \"to\": 2430}, {\"ngram\": \"a very engaging little character\", \"from\": 2462, \"to\": 2494}, {\"ngram\": \"a lot\", \"from\": 2520, \"to\": 2525}, {\"ngram\": \"people\", \"from\": 2529, \"to\": 2535}]}, {\"sentence\": \"HG: When I saw it, I thought, \\\"hello, there is a cry for help if ever I have seen one\\\".\", \"from\": 2538, \"to\": 2625, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a cry\", \"from\": 2585, \"to\": 2590}, {\"ngram\": \"help\", \"from\": 2595, \"to\": 2599}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Did you bust a few breakdancing moves in your youth, Rampaging Roy?\", \"from\": 2627, \"to\": 2694, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a few breakdancing moves\", \"from\": 2640, \"to\": 2664}, {\"ngram\": \"your youth\", \"from\": 2668, \"to\": 2678}, {\"ngram\": \"Rampaging Roy\", \"from\": 2680, \"to\": 2693}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Roy: Oh look, I do love breakdancing.\", \"from\": 2696, \"to\": 2733, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Roy\", \"from\": 2696, \"to\": 2699}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It's not something I share with others; it's something I do quietly amongst myself, in the back yard.\", \"from\": 2734, \"to\": 2835, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"something\", \"from\": 2743, \"to\": 2752}, {\"ngram\": \"others\", \"from\": 2766, \"to\": 2772}, {\"ngram\": \"something\", \"from\": 2779, \"to\": 2788}, {\"ngram\": \"the back yard\", \"from\": 2821, \"to\": 2834}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Once you get into it, it's a wonderful thing.\", \"from\": 2836, \"to\": 2881, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a wonderful thing\", \"from\": 2863, \"to\": 2880}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Great for fitness, great for balance.\", \"from\": 2882, \"to\": 2919, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"fitness\", \"from\": 2892, \"to\": 2899}, {\"ngram\": \"balance\", \"from\": 2911, \"to\": 2918}]}, {\"sentence\": \"HG: Balance!\", \"from\": 2921, \"to\": 2933, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"HG\", \"from\": 2921, \"to\": 2923}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Roy: That's what it's all about - I mean, when you put yourself on your head and spin, you come to a quick understanding of centrifugal and centripetal force, and how these forces act upon not only the head but the rest of the body.\